QuestData.Title: Delivery to Krenna
QuestData.Description: This is it, mon. Let's take these hides to Krenna and see if they pass the test.$B$BLet's hope for both our sakes Krenna doesn't notice anything.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Bundle of Hides to Krenna in Conquest Hold.
QuestData.CompletionText: Do you have any idea who you're talking to?
QuestData.RewardText: Just who do you take me for? These hides smell of flour!$B$BThis is a complete insult to the Horde!
